lyrics:
(Verse 1)
In the depths of the night, loneliness prevails,
Memories entwine, the heart in sorrow trails.
Your smile, once dreamlike and surreal,
Now remains in silence, a melancholic ordeal.

(Pre-Chorus)
A sorrowful melody echoes within,
The pain of parting, words fail to begin.
Tears of longing, falling in the dark,
Our story, like mist, fades and embarks.

(Chorus)
Oh, the melody of farewell softly plays,
The silent heart filled with tears ablaze.
The dreams of love, shattered at a touch,
The moment of goodbye, forever as such.
